name: New Year Bookings
query: select `tabNew Year Booking`.creation, `tabNew Year Booking`.name1 as "Full Name:Data:150", mobile as "Phone:Data:100", booking_for as "Party:Data:50", `tabNew Year Booking`.table as "Table", people as "People#", couple as "Couple#", female_stag as "F/Stag#", male_stag as "M/Stag#", kids as "Kids", total_amount as "Amount", total_advance as "Advance", total_balance as "Balance", coupon as Coupon, `tabIntegration Request`.status as "₹Status" from `tabNew Year Booking` LEFT JOIN `tabIntegration Request` ON `tabNew Year Booking`.name = `tabIntegration Request`.reference_docname
